For us, all the emails that we've received about people who are concerned about regulations going in on leaf blowers, I can show you an equal number, if not greater number of emails from people who are really frustrated by noise and particulate and issues with the gas powered leaf blowers, right?

450
00:45:22,801 --> 00:45:26,523
And then one other thing in here, just to talk about it too, right?

451
00:45:28,384 --> 00:45:33,168
Well, I don't have the draft right in front of me, but the draft ordinance does talk about

452
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:40,925
moving away from gas leaf blowers over a period of time for commercial, for private owners and for the city.

453
00:45:41,125 --> 00:45:45,468
So all, when we say do it for one and not other, all are included in that.

454
00:45:45,809 --> 00:45:47,510
It's all mentioned in the ordinance.

455
00:45:47,570 --> 00:45:52,334
