I hear from families, though, who say, I don't even take my kids outside anymore because it's so loud, because there's particulate blowing in the air, because I'm worried about emissions.

473
00:47:26,651 --> 00:47:33,659
And I believe them, because I have a 10-month-old son, and weekly, daily, I'm chased out of my yard.

