00:47:33,740 --> 00:47:36,943
I can't go in my yard with my 10-month-old son, because there's leaf blowers.

475
00:47:37,676 --> 00:47:41,257
in every yard around me, you know, boxed in by leaf blowers.

476
00:47:41,877 --> 00:47:42,797
And I'm sharing my truth.

477
00:47:42,897 --> 00:47:44,058
I'm sharing my experience.

478
00:47:44,898 --> 00:47:49,679
And I don't and I don't take my son out because there is particulate matter blowing in the air.

479
00:47:49,979 --> 00:47:50,579
He's 10 months.

480
00:47:52,020 --> 00:47:56,261
And I'm just going to share that I'm here to represent the voices of residents who have reached out to me.

481
00:47:56,721 --> 00:47:57,981
But I live this too.

482
00:47:58,301 --> 00:47:59,402
I live in this community as well.

