I mean, we have a representative system of government, which our job is to balance interests.

493
00:48:44,635 --> 00:48:50,037
It's to listen to you guys and to listen to the people who are concerned about the noise and air pollution.

494
00:48:51,118 --> 00:48:51,318
So.

