510
00:50:18,368 --> 00:50:25,430
So if there's some way to incentivize people to use the blowers when they are truly needed and not

511
00:50:26,737 --> 00:50:29,239
just using them because you got a tool in your hand.

512
00:50:30,540 --> 00:50:33,143
I think that would be very valuable to the community.

513
00:50:33,403 --> 00:50:35,044
I work in environmental health.

514
00:50:35,865 --> 00:50:40,830
I know how much damage noise does to children, air pollution does to children.

515
